let removeDuplicates l = 
let rec helper (seen,rest) = 
match rest with 
[] -> seen
| h::t -> 
let seen' = 
(if List.mem h seen
then seen
else h :: seen)
in
let rest' = t
in helper (seen',rest') 
in
List.rev (helper ([],l))

let pi = 4.0 *. (atan 1.0);;

let rec eval (e,x,y) =
  match e with
  | VarX  -> x
  | VarY  -> y
  | Sine a -> sin (pi * (eval (a, x, y)))
  | Cosine a -> cos (pi * (eval (a, x, y)))
  | Average (a,b) -> ((eval (a, x, y)) + (eval (b, x, y))) /. 2.
  | Times (a,b) -> (eval (a, x, y)) *. (eval (b, x, y))
  | Thresh (a,b,c,d) ->
      if (eval (a, x, y)) < (eval (b, x, y))
      then eval (c, x, y)
      else eval (d, x, y);;

let rec eval (e,x,y) =
match e with
| VarX -> x
| VarY -> y
| Sine a -> sin (pi *. eval (a,x,y))
| Cosine a -> cos (pi *. eval (a,x,y))
| Average (a,b) -> (eval(a,x,y) +. eval(b,x,y)) /. 2.
| Times (a,b) -> eval(a,x,y) *. eval(b,x,y)
| Thresh (a,b,c,d) -> if eval(a,x,y) < eval(b,x,y) then eval(c,x,y) else eval(d,x,y)
